Interface XDSQuery

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XDSQueryPersonTimeInterval, XDSQueryPersonTimeIntervalTreatment, XDSQueryPersonTimeIntervalType

    public interface XDSQuery
    A marker interface. Implementing classes define a small set of valid queries that can be formulated and executed against the XDS repository.
